1
00:00:05,703 --> 00:00:08,399
<i>Press down hard on the gas</i>

2
00:00:08,472 --> 00:00:12,340
<i>That's right, there's no compromise</i>

3
00:00:12,410 --> 00:00:16,403
<i>We'll slip through the night</i>

4
00:00:16,747 --> 00:00:19,238
<i>At the final moment push hard</i>

5
00:00:19,317 --> 00:00:23,378
<i>That's right, all the way to zero,</i>

6
00:00:23,454 --> 00:00:27,413
<i>Until we wipe away the days</i>

7
00:00:28,893 --> 00:00:33,626
<i>Gently open your heart</i>

8
00:00:34,332 --> 00:00:37,301
<i>If you pull it close to you</i>

9
00:00:39,737 --> 00:00:41,830
<i>It will reach you, without a doubt</i>

10
00:00:42,573 --> 00:00:43,870
<i>It will come, closer</i>

11
00:00:44,208 --> 00:00:46,768
<i>Now</i>

12
00:00:54,819 --> 00:01:00,189
<i>We're speeding through life,</i>
<i>squeezing it for all of its worth</i>

13
00:01:00,391 --> 00:01:01,551
<i>Our feet are tied</i>

14
00:01:01,625 --> 00:01:05,425
<i>But we still keep going farther</i>

15
00:01:05,763 --> 00:01:10,962
<i>Even if I take it back, and grasp it</i>

16
00:01:11,235 --> 00:01:12,566
<i>If you're not the one</i>

17
00:01:12,636 --> 00:01:14,035
<i>There will be no meaning</i>

18
00:01:14,105 --> 00:01:20,374
<i>And so we'll go far off into the distance.</i>

19
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:39,210
It's a custom where balance is preserved
by fighting and removing life.

20
00:01:39,284 --> 00:01:42,082
This is the friendship
of the Shinobi world.

21
00:01:42,154 --> 00:01:44,748
This is a fight for life with the pride
of the village and

22
00:01:44,823 --> 00:01:47,348
one's own dream on the line.

23
00:01:48,326 --> 00:01:50,920
Heh, I'm convinced.

24
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:52,892
Anything is fine.

25
00:01:53,298 --> 00:01:58,361
Just tell us the content
of that fight for life test.

26
00:01:58,603 --> 00:01:59,228
Very well.

27
00:01:59,337 --> 00:02:03,933
Now then, this is where I'd
like to explain the third exam.

28
00:02:04,009 --> 00:02:05,306
But actually...

29
00:02:08,313 --> 00:02:13,876
Please allow me, Hayate Gekko who was
given the task of judge, to speak first.

30
00:02:14,152 --> 00:02:15,483
I leave it to you...

31
00:02:16,755 --> 00:02:19,588
There's something... I'd like you all
to do...

32
00:02:21,426 --> 00:02:23,587
before the third exam.

33
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:32,192
And that is a preliminary
to the third exam,

34
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:34,966
with participation in
the main battle on the line.

35
00:02:37,476 --> 00:02:38,238
Preliminary?

36
00:02:38,510 --> 00:02:41,308
What do you mean... preliminary?!

37
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:46,078
Sensei, I don't understand
the point of that preliminary.

38
00:02:46,785 --> 00:02:50,915
Why aren't we doing the next exam
with the remaining test takers?

39
00:02:51,590 --> 00:02:53,615
This time around,

40
00:02:53,692 --> 00:02:56,820
perhaps because the first and
second exams were easy,

41
00:02:57,429 --> 00:03:00,830
there are a few too many
people left, you see.

42
00:03:01,700 --> 00:03:04,362
In accordance with the rules
of the Chunin Exams,

43
00:03:04,836 --> 00:03:08,169
a preliminary will be held in order to
reduce the number advancing.

44
00:03:09,407 --> 00:03:10,806
N-No way!

45
00:03:11,676 --> 00:03:14,440
As Lord Hokage said before,

46
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:18,941
many guests will be coming
to the third exam.

47
00:03:19,651 --> 00:03:24,350
So we can't have long pointless matches
and our time is limited as well.

48
00:03:25,524 --> 00:03:29,893
Therefore, those of you
not in top physical condition...

49
00:03:31,429 --> 00:03:34,023
<i>Hey, is he okay...?!</i>

50
00:03:34,499 --> 00:03:37,593
<i>The teacher doesn't look well himself?!</i>

51
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:38,929
Excuse me.

52
00:03:39,571 --> 00:03:44,702
Those of you who wish to drop out,
please speak up now.

53
00:03:45,443 --> 00:03:47,968
The preliminary will
begin immediately, so...

54
00:03:48,246 --> 00:03:49,838
Immediately, you say...?!

55
00:03:49,915 --> 00:03:54,079
But we finally made it through
the second exam.

56
00:03:54,352 --> 00:03:56,217
This is a pain...

57
00:03:56,288 --> 00:03:58,688
Huh? What about our meal?

58
00:04:00,926 --> 00:04:06,831
<i>Narrowing the Field.</i>
<i>Sudden Death Elimination!</i>

59
00:04:08,967 --> 00:04:10,332
<i>Okay!</i>

60
00:04:10,735 --> 00:04:12,726
<i>I'm going to do my best, no matter what!</i>

61
00:04:13,138 --> 00:04:15,129
<i>I promised Kabuto, too...</i>

62
00:04:17,108 --> 00:04:17,699
And oh...

63
00:04:18,076 --> 00:04:23,013
I forgot to mention this, but it will
be individual battles from now on.

64
00:04:23,682 --> 00:04:27,709
It is your decision, so feel free
to raise your hands and drop out.

65
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,478
<i>Who's going to quit?!</i>

66
00:04:33,458 --> 00:04:34,254
Sasuke?!

67
00:04:36,294 --> 00:04:39,457
<i>The waves of pain are</i>
<i>coming faster...</i>

68
00:04:41,900 --> 00:04:43,731
<i>Sasuke... I knew it.</i>

69
00:04:44,235 --> 00:04:48,035
Sasuke, you should quit
these preliminaries!

70
00:04:49,207 --> 00:04:49,798
Huh?!

71
00:04:50,275 --> 00:04:52,505
L-Look, you haven't been yourself

72
00:04:52,577 --> 00:04:55,273
ever since you got worked
over by that Orochimaru guy!

73
00:04:56,781 --> 00:04:59,579
That bruise hurts even now, right...?

74
00:05:00,986 --> 00:05:01,782
<i>Bruise...?</i>

75
00:05:02,621 --> 00:05:03,849
At this rate...!

76
00:05:10,829 --> 00:05:13,127
<i>I gave him a parting gift.</i>

77
00:05:13,698 --> 00:05:18,328
<i>Sasuke will definitely seek me...</i>
<i>in search of power.</i>

78
00:05:34,419 --> 00:05:36,478
<i>You're the only one left.</i>

79
00:05:39,357 --> 00:05:40,016
Please...

80
00:05:42,861 --> 00:05:45,159
Please, quit!

81
00:05:46,731 --> 00:05:48,892
I'm... scared.

82
00:05:51,503 --> 00:05:52,333
<i>Sakura...</i>

83
00:05:56,808 --> 00:05:58,105
I knew it.

84
00:05:59,077 --> 00:06:00,271
What shall we do?

85
00:06:00,679 --> 00:06:02,670
We should remove him
from the exams

86
00:06:02,747 --> 00:06:05,011
and isolate him with
Anbu bodyguards on him.

87
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:07,279
We should recommend that
he retire immediately.

88
00:06:07,352 --> 00:06:12,085
He's not the kind of type to
just obey like that...?!

89
00:06:13,358 --> 00:06:16,384
After all, he's of the Uchiha clan.

90
00:06:16,528 --> 00:06:18,519
What're you talking nonsense for?!

91
00:06:18,730 --> 00:06:20,493
I'll make him stop, by force if needed!

92
00:06:20,665 --> 00:06:23,566
The Curse Mark responds even
when one's just building up Chakra

93
00:06:23,635 --> 00:06:25,899
and attempts to forcibly
extract his strength!

94
00:06:26,671 --> 00:06:29,799
It's a prohibited Jutsu that eats
into the body of the one who uses a Jutsu!

95
00:06:31,876 --> 00:06:34,071
It's a wonder that kid is even enduring it.

96
00:06:36,014 --> 00:06:38,278
He should really already be dead!

97
00:06:39,017 --> 00:06:40,143
Lord Hokage!

98
00:06:42,921 --> 00:06:46,448
You're in no condition to
fight properly, Sasuke...!

99
00:06:46,691 --> 00:06:47,680
Shut up.

100
00:06:48,159 --> 00:06:49,592
I understand!

101
00:06:50,395 --> 00:06:51,623
Be quiet!

102
00:06:51,796 --> 00:06:54,560
But you've been enduring the pain
this whole time, right?!

103
00:06:55,867 --> 00:06:57,300
<i>Please</i> be quiet!

104
00:06:58,203 --> 00:06:59,932
No matter what you say, Sasuke...

105
00:07:00,739 --> 00:07:02,934
I'm going to tell the teachers
about the bruise!

106
00:07:04,409 --> 00:07:05,137
If I do that...

107
00:07:08,513 --> 00:07:09,537
Well...

108
00:07:10,315 --> 00:07:11,009
Oh...?!

109
00:07:11,449 --> 00:07:12,507
What...?

110
00:07:16,454 --> 00:07:19,218
Excuse me... I'll quit.

111
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:24,160
K-Kabuto...?

112
00:07:28,133 --> 00:07:30,101
Let's see...

113
00:07:32,170 --> 00:07:35,162
Kabuto Yakushi of
the Leaf Village, correct?

114
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,870
Then, you may step back.

115
00:07:38,543 --> 00:07:39,407
Okay.

116
00:07:40,912 --> 00:07:41,708
Kabuto!

117
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:43,975
Why're you quitting?!

118
00:07:44,315 --> 00:07:46,545
Tell me! Why?!

119
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,846
<i>This guy...</i>

120
00:07:51,122 --> 00:07:52,919
I'm sorry, Naruto...

121
00:07:53,725 --> 00:07:56,853
But my body is worn out.

122
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:01,660
Actually before the first exam...

123
00:08:01,733 --> 00:08:03,598
when I wrangled with
the guys from Sound Village

124
00:08:04,068 --> 00:08:06,593
I've had no hearing at all in my left ear.

125
00:08:08,273 --> 00:08:10,241
To fight right away...

126
00:08:10,975 --> 00:08:14,570
and to be told that my life would
also be on the line, I can't go on.

127
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:24,816
I've seen that face a few times.

128
00:08:25,557 --> 00:08:30,290
As I recall, I think he dropped out
of the main battle before, as well.

129
00:08:31,129 --> 00:08:33,359
What in the world is he thinking?

130
00:08:34,766 --> 00:08:35,562
Anko.

131
00:08:36,067 --> 00:08:37,125
Uh... yes.

132
00:08:39,637 --> 00:08:41,002
Kabuto Yakushi.

133
00:08:41,906 --> 00:08:45,034
According to the data,
he has failed six straight times.

134
00:08:46,711 --> 00:08:48,440
What about his background?

135
00:08:49,414 --> 00:08:50,745
From his time at the Academy,

136
00:08:50,815 --> 00:08:52,646
he was a student who did
not really stand out,

137
00:08:52,717 --> 00:08:54,150
and his grades were ordinary.

138
00:08:54,652 --> 00:08:57,348
He finally passed the graduation
exam on his third try.

139
00:08:58,256 --> 00:09:00,019
After that, as for the missions
he carried out,

140
00:09:00,091 --> 00:09:03,254
two C-ranks and fourteen D-ranks.

141
00:09:03,895 --> 00:09:06,523
It's not a battle record to
write home about.

142
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:09,562
However...

143
00:09:10,668 --> 00:09:11,657
However?

144
00:09:11,903 --> 00:09:14,599
It's about before the Academy.

145
00:09:14,939 --> 00:09:15,667
Hmm?

146
00:09:16,507 --> 00:09:18,031
Do you remember the story...

147
00:09:18,109 --> 00:09:23,513
about the one boy brought back
from the Kikyo Pass battle?

148
00:09:24,916 --> 00:09:26,213
I remember.

149
00:09:26,751 --> 00:09:30,710
As I recall, I heard an enemy boy survivor
at the battlefield

150
00:09:30,955 --> 00:09:35,551
was taken back by a Jonin from
the medical unit.

151
00:09:35,827 --> 00:09:38,318
So he's that boy...?

152
00:09:39,163 --> 00:09:41,063
Don't take arbitrary actions.

153
00:09:41,532 --> 00:09:44,057
Have you forgotten
Orochimaru's orders?

154
00:09:45,336 --> 00:09:46,963
I leave it to you guys.

155
00:09:47,872 --> 00:09:48,930
You in particular, Yoroi.

156
00:09:49,974 --> 00:09:53,410
There should be no problems
here with your ability.

157
00:09:55,647 --> 00:09:58,241
This is where you can
show your strength.

158
00:09:58,783 --> 00:10:03,482
Those of you who are irritated that
I'm ahead of you.

159
00:10:04,088 --> 00:10:07,023
So you're Orochimaru's favorite, huh?

160
00:10:07,659 --> 00:10:09,388
Don't get all high and mighty, kid.

161
00:10:10,028 --> 00:10:12,121
I understand, Yoroi sir.

162
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:19,429
Oh.

163
00:10:21,306 --> 00:10:23,740
<i>Naruto... Sasuke...</i>

164
00:10:24,609 --> 00:10:27,339
<i>I wanted to play with you guys</i>
<i>a little more.</i>

165
00:10:28,446 --> 00:10:29,777
<i>But if I do more than this...</i>

166
00:10:30,381 --> 00:10:32,611
<i>The old me might get stirred up.</i>

167
00:10:34,018 --> 00:10:36,282
<i>I am a spy so far as it goes.</i>

168
00:10:37,155 --> 00:10:40,420
<i>I cannot expose myself, here.</i>

169
00:10:41,926 --> 00:10:44,724
<i>Also...if you are going to watch.</i>

170
00:10:45,463 --> 00:10:48,296
<i>My role of information collecting</i>
<i>has served its purpose...</i>

171
00:10:49,367 --> 00:10:50,664
<i>Master Orochimaru.</i>

172
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:56,036
<i>I'll save the fun, for some other time...</i>

173
00:10:57,141 --> 00:10:58,369
<i>Sasuke...</i>

174
00:10:59,477 --> 00:11:00,671
<i>And Naruto...</i>

175
00:11:01,846 --> 00:11:02,710
<i>You too.</i>

176
00:11:17,626 --> 00:11:21,357
Now then, there are no others
who will quit?

177
00:11:24,199 --> 00:11:27,225
<i>I must tell the teachers,</i>
<i>about Sasuke's bruise!</i>

178
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,272
Huh?!

179
00:11:33,942 --> 00:11:36,137
Be quiet about this bruise.

180
00:11:43,552 --> 00:11:45,543
Why're you acting tough like that?!

181
00:11:46,121 --> 00:11:48,885
I don't want to watch you suffer
all the time anymore!

182
00:11:49,591 --> 00:11:51,058
For me you are!

183
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,851
This has nothing to do with you!

184
00:11:56,031 --> 00:11:57,692
It's none of your business.

185
00:12:03,605 --> 00:12:05,300
I said it once before...

186
00:12:09,745 --> 00:12:11,440
I'm an avenger.

187
00:12:12,914 --> 00:12:16,179
This is not just a mere exam to me.

188
00:12:16,585 --> 00:12:20,180
The Chunin business has
nothing to do with me.

189
00:12:23,959 --> 00:12:28,487
"Am I strong?"
All I want is the answer to that.

190
00:12:29,264 --> 00:12:31,323
By fighting with those who are strong

191
00:12:31,667 --> 00:12:32,759
And...

192
00:12:34,403 --> 00:12:36,803
<i>I'm Gaara of the desert.</i>

193
00:12:37,372 --> 00:12:40,239
<i>Hey, you there...</i>
<i>Identify yourself.</i>

194
00:12:41,043 --> 00:12:42,032
<i>I declare.</i>

195
00:12:42,444 --> 00:12:45,072
<i>You are absolutely no match for me.</i>

196
00:12:46,048 --> 00:12:50,109
<i>If I have the opportunity to fight you</i>
<i>in the next exam,</i>

197
00:12:50,452 --> 00:12:53,046
<i>we won't run or hide.</i>

198
00:12:54,222 --> 00:12:57,988
And they're... here!

199
00:13:02,698 --> 00:13:07,362
I will not allow even you
to take my path away from me!

200
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:10,164
Sasuke...

201
00:13:10,906 --> 00:13:12,134
You!

202
00:13:12,207 --> 00:13:14,767
What're you doing putting up
a front, you idiot?!

203
00:13:14,843 --> 00:13:16,504
Here Sakura is this worried about you...!

204
00:13:16,578 --> 00:13:17,510
Naruto!

205
00:13:19,815 --> 00:13:22,340
I want to fight you, too.

206
00:13:22,651 --> 00:13:23,447
Huh?!

207
00:13:31,727 --> 00:13:34,719
What Orochimaru said
is sitting on my mind.

208
00:13:35,230 --> 00:13:37,357
I will let Sasuke do the test...

209
00:13:37,566 --> 00:13:38,726
- and see how things go.
- Wha?!

210
00:13:39,034 --> 00:13:40,501
L-Lord Hokage...!

211
00:13:41,436 --> 00:13:44,303
However, if the Curse Mark opens

212
00:13:44,373 --> 00:13:47,001
and the power gets even a little bit
out of control,

213
00:13:47,075 --> 00:13:48,269
get in there and stop it.

214
00:13:48,443 --> 00:13:49,171
All right.

215
00:13:49,611 --> 00:13:50,339
But!

216
00:13:53,014 --> 00:13:54,072
I understand.

217
00:14:00,655 --> 00:14:04,455
Now then, we will begin the preliminaries.

218
00:14:05,794 --> 00:14:08,592
The preliminaries to come
will be one on one individual battles.

219
00:14:09,631 --> 00:14:13,158
In other words,
actual battle format.

220
00:14:15,070 --> 00:14:19,370
There are now exactly twenty people,
so we will conduct ten battles.

221
00:14:20,175 --> 00:14:24,168
The winners will be able to
advance to the third exam.

222
00:14:25,046 --> 00:14:26,570
There are no rules at all.

223
00:14:27,149 --> 00:14:33,577
You will fight until someone dies,
collapses... or admits defeat.

224
00:14:34,489 --> 00:14:39,051
And... please admit defeat right away
if you don't want to die.

225
00:14:39,561 --> 00:14:44,225
However, in case I judge
that a match is over...

226
00:14:46,168 --> 00:14:49,899
err... I don't want to needlessly increase
dead bodies,

227
00:14:49,971 --> 00:14:52,303
so I will intervene and stop the match
or something to that effect.

228
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:55,743
What holds the key to your destinies is...

229
00:14:59,448 --> 00:15:00,210
Open it.

230
00:15:10,258 --> 00:15:11,350
This.

231
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:16,529
The names of two foes will be
randomly selected and

232
00:15:16,598 --> 00:15:20,159
displayed on this electronic signboard.

233
00:15:22,003 --> 00:15:24,233
Now then, let's get right down to it

234
00:15:24,372 --> 00:15:27,830
and announce the two names
for the first battle.

235
00:15:38,353 --> 00:15:40,651
Yoroi Akado vs. Sasuke Uchiha

236
00:15:41,490 --> 00:15:44,391
<i>To think it'd be so soon...?!</i>

237
00:15:48,530 --> 00:15:50,122
I couldn't ask for more.

238
00:15:50,732 --> 00:15:51,596
No way!

239
00:15:52,033 --> 00:15:53,330
Why Sasuke?!

240
00:16:01,042 --> 00:16:04,534
Now then, the two displayed on
the signboard, come forward.

241
00:16:10,585 --> 00:16:16,353
For the 1st battle, Yoroi Akado and
Sasuke Uchiha have been selected.

242
00:16:17,325 --> 00:16:18,815
No objections, right?

243
00:16:19,895 --> 00:16:20,691
- Right.
- No!

244
00:16:32,374 --> 00:16:34,865
<i>All I can do now is watch...</i>

245
00:16:36,378 --> 00:16:37,436
<i>Sasuke...</i>

246
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,208
<i>Sasuke!</i>

247
00:16:39,581 --> 00:16:43,278
<i>If you want to fight me, don't lose!</i>

248
00:16:44,119 --> 00:16:47,577
<i>Sasuke... You're acting strange...</i>

249
00:16:48,590 --> 00:16:50,217
<i>Is it because of the Curse Mark...?</i>

250
00:16:51,126 --> 00:16:53,424
<i>Sasuke, do your best!</i>

251
00:16:54,396 --> 00:16:56,523
<i>I guess I'll wait and see...</i>

252
00:17:00,201 --> 00:17:01,600
<i>The pain won't go away!</i>

253
00:17:03,672 --> 00:17:05,640
<i>It appears the Curse Mark hurts.</i>

254
00:17:06,274 --> 00:17:10,472
Now then, we will begin the first battle.

255
00:17:13,381 --> 00:17:18,580
Everyone other than the two foes,
please move to the upper area.

256
00:17:29,564 --> 00:17:31,828
Hey! Kakashi Sensei!

257
00:17:33,902 --> 00:17:34,698
Sasuke!

258
00:17:35,136 --> 00:17:35,864
Huh?

259
00:17:37,973 --> 00:17:39,406
Don't use the Sharingan.

260
00:17:41,776 --> 00:17:42,936
So you knew?

261
00:17:44,145 --> 00:17:46,306
If that Curse Mark on your neck
gets out of control,

262
00:17:46,948 --> 00:17:48,643
it could endanger your life.

263
00:17:50,585 --> 00:17:51,574
I believe it.

264
00:17:52,787 --> 00:17:55,779
Well, the match will be
called off at that time.

265
00:17:56,458 --> 00:17:59,018
I'll be coming in to stop it,
so good luck.

266
00:18:00,528 --> 00:18:01,586
<i>Called off, you say?!</i>

267
00:18:04,633 --> 00:18:08,967
<i>It seems this Curse Mark thing</i>
<i>is responding to my Chakra.</i>

268
00:18:15,577 --> 00:18:19,308
<i>This is my final Chakra...</i>

269
00:18:19,948 --> 00:18:21,040
<i>Sharingan!</i>

270
00:18:27,255 --> 00:18:30,156
<i>Sasuke, stop using the Sharingan!</i>

271
00:18:31,092 --> 00:18:33,083
<i>If I carelessly build up Chakra,</i>

272
00:18:33,294 --> 00:18:34,921
<i>it would extract my spirit energy,</i>

273
00:18:34,996 --> 00:18:37,863
<i>and bring out the Chakra</i>
<i>inside my body to no end.</i>

274
00:18:40,902 --> 00:18:42,597
<i>In other words, in this match,</i>

275
00:18:42,837 --> 00:18:47,672
<i>I can hardly use even my regular Jutsu,</i>
<i>not to mention the Sharingan!</i>

276
00:18:50,879 --> 00:18:58,411
<i>However... Yoroi's ability is</i>
<i>the worst for you, Sasuke.</i>

277
00:19:04,693 --> 00:19:07,355
<i>Now then... How will I go...?</i>

278
00:19:19,407 --> 00:19:22,103
<i>Don't act rashly...Sasuke.</i>

279
00:19:23,178 --> 00:19:25,544
Now then, please begin.

280
00:19:25,914 --> 00:19:27,609
Let's go!

281
00:19:28,349 --> 00:19:29,213
Yeah!

282
00:19:46,334 --> 00:19:47,232
<i>Oh no!</i>

283
00:19:58,713 --> 00:19:59,941
He did it!

284
00:20:08,123 --> 00:20:09,613
<i>My strength...?!</i>

285
00:20:21,636 --> 00:20:22,466
<i>W-What is this?</i>

286
00:20:22,804 --> 00:20:25,602
<i>My body strength has suddenly...!</i>

287
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:29,408
Sasuke!

288
00:20:46,394 --> 00:20:47,122
<i>Sasuke...!</i>

289
00:20:48,229 --> 00:20:50,823
You... my Chakra...

290
00:20:53,201 --> 00:20:54,828
You just noticed now...?

291
00:21:05,734 --> 00:21:10,330
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

292
00:21:10,439 --> 00:21:18,539
<i>The clear, blue sky goes on and on</i>

293
00:21:19,615 --> 00:21:28,148
<i>The ocean spans limitlessly</i>

294
00:21:28,757 --> 00:21:36,459
<i>Please keep that smile on your face forever</i>

295
00:21:37,866 --> 00:21:43,395
<i>Or else I'll cry</i>

296
00:21:43,472 --> 00:21:47,238
<i>You won't have to search around you</i>

297
00:21:47,309 --> 00:21:50,870
<i>It's all ok now.</i>

298
00:21:51,347 --> 00:21:59,755
<i>Everyone is inside</i>
<i>this hand</i>

299
00:22:00,089 --> 00:22:05,152
<i>when you want to cry, and you want to run away</i>

300
00:22:05,294 --> 00:22:09,697
<i>When you forget what happiness is</i>

301
00:22:09,865 --> 00:22:13,528
<i>Just sing.</i>

302
00:22:13,836 --> 00:22:18,933
<i>Light is born, and darkness was born</i>

303
00:22:19,074 --> 00:22:21,201
<i>The two are one</i>

304
00:22:21,310 --> 00:22:27,579
<i>Harmonia, feel the telepathy</i>

305
00:22:28,183 --> 00:22:33,177
<i>Hey, can you hear it?</i>

306
00:22:37,867 --> 00:22:40,199
Damn it!
The pain won't go away!

307
00:22:40,636 --> 00:22:43,764
This damned Curse Mark is
responding all the time!

308
00:22:44,140 --> 00:22:47,234
But I won't let this
exam get called off!

309
00:22:47,677 --> 00:22:49,907
How will I do?
How should I fight?

310
00:22:50,546 --> 00:22:51,979
Am I strong?

311
00:22:52,215 --> 00:22:54,046
All I want is the answer to that.

312
00:22:54,384 --> 00:22:57,717
I won't let this thing swallow me up
in a place like this!

313
00:22:58,554 --> 00:23:02,183
Next episode: "Bushy-Brow's Jealousy...
Lions Barrage Unleashed!"
